✅ How This Script Works
1️⃣ Asks the user for:

The real website URL
Keywords to check for fake sites
TLDs to scan for suspicious domains
2️⃣ Checks if fake sites exist in phishing databases (OpenPhish, URLhaus).
3️⃣ Performs a WHOIS lookup to check domain registration.
4️⃣ Scrapes and compares website content for similarity.
5️⃣ Generates a PDF report if phishing is detected.

✅ How to Run the Script
1️⃣ Install dependencies:

bash
Copy
Edit
python3 -m pip install requests beautifulsoup4 python-whois pdfkit difflib html5lib
2️⃣ Run the script:

bash
Copy
Edit
python3 phishing_detector.py
3️⃣ Enter the real website, keywords, and TLDs when prompted.
4️⃣ Phishing detection begins automatically!
